---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Custom AI Development | Intelio">
  <!-- HERO SECTION with EXISTING VIDEO -->
  <section class="hero" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)), url('/logos/Cinematic_Liquid_Metal_Wave_Animation.mp4');">
    <video autoplay muted loop playsinline style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; z-index: 0;">
      <source src="/logos/Cinematic_Liquid_Metal_Wave_Animation.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    </video>
    <div class="hero-content" style="position: relative; z-index: 1;">
      <div class="hero-label">CUSTOM AI DEVELOPMENT</div>
      <h1>Custom AI Development</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Purpose-built platforms engineered for competitive advantage. Deal sourcing, system integration, and data infrastructure at the speed you need. Built specifically for how your business operates.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <button class="btn btn-primary">Build with us</button>
        <button class="btn btn-secondary">Learn more →</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- INTRO SECTION with IMAGE -->
  <section class="intro-section light-bg">
    <div class="intro-text">
      <p class="intro-primary">Custom software becomes competitive advantage when it encodes your specific operational logic.</p>
      <p>We architect and build production-grade systems. Data infrastructure, application logic, intelligent automation, user interfaces—engineered as integrated platforms designed for scale. AI integrated at the architectural level where it removes friction, improves decisions, or creates new capabilities.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="image-placeholder">
      <div class="image-placeholder-text">
        <p style="font-weight: 600;">ARCHITECTURE DIAGRAM</p>
        <p style="font-size: 0.9rem;">System Overview</p>
        <p style="font-size: 0.75rem; margin-top: 1rem; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);">600x400px</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- KEY STATS SECTION -->
  <section class="stats-section">
    <div class="section-label">REAL OUTCOMES</div>
    <h2>The impact of custom systems</h2>
    
    <div class="stats-callout">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-value">3-5x</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Faster decision velocity with integrated automation</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-value">60%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Reduction in manual, repetitive work</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-value">100%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Code ownership. Zero vendor lock-in.</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="section-supporting-text">Organizations building custom systems create competitive advantage through operational logic generic platforms cannot capture. Systems that become so essential to how you work, switching to alternatives becomes impossible.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE BUILD -->
  <section id="capabilities" class="capabilities-section">
    <div class="section-label">WHAT WE BUILD</div>
    <h2>Systems engineered from ground up</h2>
    
    <div class="capabilities-grid">
      <!-- Full-Stack Systems -->
      <div class="capability-card">
        <div class="capability-icon">ICON 1</div>
        <h3>Full-Stack Systems</h3>
        <p>Complete production systems from database to user interface. Data models architected for scale. APIs designed for reliability and integration.</p>
        <div class="capability-details">
          <div class="detail-item"><span class="emphasis">Tech:</span> PostgreSQL, Supabase, Node.js, React, Vue</div>
          <div class="detail-item"><span class="emphasis">Built for:</span> Operational platforms, customer applications, admin tooling</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Intelligent Automation -->
      <div class="capability-card">
        <div class="capability-icon">ICON 2</div>
        <h3>Intelligent Automation</h3>
        <p>Systems with AI integrated at the architectural level. Language models process information. Machine learning predicts outcomes. Automation handles decisions.</p>
        <div class="capability-details">
          <div class="detail-item"><span class="emphasis">Tech:</span> Claude API, n8n, TensorFlow, scikit-learn</div>
          <div class="detail-item"><span class="emphasis">Powers:</span> Deal matching, churn prediction, document intelligence</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SaaS & Product -->
      <div class="capability-card">
        <div class="capability-icon">ICON 3</div>
        <h3>SaaS & Product Platforms</h3>
        <p>Multi-tenant platforms engineered for scale, security, and efficient operations. Subscription infrastructure with billing and metering.</p>
        <div class="capability-details">
          <div class="detail-item"><span class="emphasis">Tech:</span> Scalable architecture, secure APIs, SOC 2 compliance</div>
          <div class="detail-item"><span class="emphasis">Includes:</span> Billing, analytics, real-time dashboards</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Enterprise Infrastructure -->
      <div class="capability-card">
        <div class="capability-icon">ICON 4</div>
        <h3>Enterprise Infrastructure</h3>
        <p>Complex implementations connecting multiple systems, modernizing legacy architecture, and creating unified operational visibility across departments.</p>
        <div class="capability-details">
          <div class="detail-item"><span class="emphasis">Tech:</span> Data integration, API orchestration, migration</div>
          <div class="detail-item"><span class="emphasis">Delivers:</span> Cross-system integration, legacy modernization</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TECHNICAL APPROACH with ALTERNATING IMAGES -->
  <section id="approach" class="approach-section">
    <div class="section-label">OUR TECHNICAL APPROACH</div>
    <h2>How we engineer custom systems</h2>
    
    <div class="approach-item">
      <div class="approach-content">
        <div class="approach-step">
          <h3>01. Define the Problem</h3>
          <p>Comprehensive discovery to understand what you're building, what outcomes matter, and what success looks like. We understand workflows, bottlenecks, decision points, and edge cases deeply. <span class="emphasis">Clear scope definition before development begins.</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="approach-image">IMAGE 1</div>
    </div>

    <div class="approach-item approach-item-reverse">
      <div class="approach-content">
        <div class="approach-step">
          <h3>02. Architect the System</h3>
          <p>Complete system design—data models, API architecture, integration points, automation logic, user interfaces. Architecture designed for production: scalability, security, reliability. <span class="emphasis">You review and approve architecture before build.</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="approach-image">IMAGE 2</div>
    </div>

    <div class="approach-item">
      <div class="approach-content">
        <div class="approach-step">
          <h3>03. Build in Iterations</h3>
          <p>Iterative development with continuous visibility. Working systems delivered every sprint. Code reviews and testing built into every cycle. <span class="emphasis">No prototypes. Production-ready code.</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="approach-image">IMAGE 3</div>
    </div>

    <div class="approach-item approach-item-reverse">
      <div class="approach-content">
        <div class="approach-step">
          <h3>04. Deploy & Transition</h3>
          <p>Deployment to your infrastructure with complete infrastructure code. Monitoring, logging, backup, disaster recovery. Comprehensive documentation. <span class="emphasis">Complete code ownership and IP transfer.</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="approach-image">IMAGE 4</div>
    </div>

    <!-- TECHNICAL STACK -->
    <div class="stack-section">
      <h3 class="stack-title">Technical Capabilities & Stack</h3>
      
      <div class="stack-category">
        <h4>Architecture & Infrastructure</h4>
        <div class="stack-items">
          <div class="stack-item">PostgreSQL / Supabase</div>
          <div class="stack-item">RESTful & GraphQL APIs</div>
          <div class="stack-item">Docker & CI/CD</div>
          <div class="stack-item">Vercel / Railway / AWS</div>
          <div class="stack-item">SOC 2 Compliance</div>
          <div class="stack-item">Infrastructure-as-Code</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="stack-category">
        <h4>Application Development</h4>
        <div class="stack-items">
          <div class="stack-item">React / Vue / Astro</div>
          <div class="stack-item">Node.js / Python</div>
          <div class="stack-item">Real-Time Websockets</div>
          <div class="stack-item">Responsive Design</div>
          <div class="stack-item">Performance Optimization</div>
          <div class="stack-item">Accessibility Standards</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="stack-category">
        <h4>AI & Intelligent Automation</h4>
        <div class="stack-items">
          <div class="stack-item">Claude API</div>
          <div class="stack-item">Machine Learning Models</div>
          <div class="stack-item">n8n Workflows</div>
          <div class="stack-item">Document Intelligence</div>
          <div class="stack-item">Predictive Analytics</div>
          <div class="stack-item">Anomaly Detection</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="stack-category">
        <h4>Integration & Data</h4>
        <div class="stack-items">
          <div class="stack-item">Salesforce</div>
          <div class="stack-item">HubSpot / Dynamics</div>
          <div class="stack-item">Power Platform</div>
          <div class="stack-item">ETL Pipelines</div>
          <div class="stack-item">Real-Time Analytics</div>
          <div class="stack-item">Data Transformation</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="stack-category">
        <h4>Microsoft Ecosystem</h4>
        <div class="stack-items">
          <div class="stack-item">Power Apps</div>
          <div class="stack-item">Power Automate</div>
          <div class="stack-item">Power BI</div>
          <div class="stack-item">Dynamics 365</div>
          <div class="stack-item">Logic Apps</div>
          <div class="stack-item">Teams / SharePoint</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SUCCESS STORIES / CASE STUDIES -->
  <section class="case-studies-section light-bg">
    <div class="section-label">SUCCESS IN CUSTOM SYSTEMS</div>
    <h2>Real outcomes from organizations we've built for</h2>
    
    <div class="case-studies-grid">
      <a href="#" class="case-study-card">
        <div class="case-study-image">IMAGE 1</div>
        <div class="case-study-content">
          <div class="case-study-label">INVESTMENT FIRM</div>
          <div class="case-study-title">Deal matching system accelerates evaluation by 67%</div>
          <div class="case-study-description">Built unified deal intelligence platform connecting brokers, automating underwriting, providing real-time visibility.</div>
          <div class="case-study-metric">6-day reduction in cycle time →</div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="#" class="case-study-card">
        <div class="case-study-image">IMAGE 2</div>
        <div class="case-study-content">
          <div class="case-study-label">SAAS COMPANY</div>
          <div class="case-study-title">Retention intelligence closes 40% more deals</div>
          <div class="case-study-description">Implemented AI-powered churn prediction and automated retention workflows. Increased deal flow 3x while maintaining quality.</div>
          <div class="case-study-metric">40% more qualified deals →</div>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a href="#" class="case-study-card">
        <div class="case-study-image">IMAGE 3</div>
        <div class="case-study-content">
          <div class="case-study-label">PORTFOLIO FIRM</div>
          <div class="case-study-title">Eliminates manual reporting overhead completely</div>
          <div class="case-study-description">Automated reporting system generates portfolio performance reports on-demand. Reports that took 3-5 days now generate in minutes.</div>
          <div class="case-study-metric">Zero manual effort →</div>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY SYSTEMS MATTER -->
  <section class="comparison-section">
    <div class="section-label">WHY SYSTEMS MATTER</div>
    <h2>The advantage of built systems</h2>
    
    <div class="comparison-grid">
      <div class="comparison-card">
        <h4>Off-The-Shelf Problem</h4>
        <div class="comparison-item">
          <div class="comparison-label">GENERIC OPTIMIZATION</div>
          <div class="comparison-text">Optimized for broad use cases. You adapt your business to fit the software.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="comparison-item">
          <div class="comparison-label">VENDOR DEPENDENCY</div>
          <div class="comparison-text">Roadmap depends on vendor. New features = waiting or paying for customization.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="comparison-item">
          <div class="comparison-label">COMPETITIVE PARITY</div>
          <div class="comparison-text">Competitors use the same software. No competitive advantage in the platform itself.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="comparison-card comparison-card-cyan">
        <h4>Custom Systems Advantage</h4>
        <div class="comparison-item">
          <div class="comparison-label">ENCODED LOGIC</div>
          <div class="comparison-text">Your workflows and decision rules become system architecture—not configuration.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="comparison-item">
          <div class="comparison-label">COMPLETE OWNERSHIP</div>
          <div class="comparison-text">You own code, infrastructure, IP. Your roadmap is your roadmap.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="comparison-item">
          <div class="comparison-label">COMPETITIVE MOAT</div>
          <div class="comparison-text">Systems encoding your specific logic create advantage competitors can't buy.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- COMMITMENTS -->
  <section class="commitments-section">
    <div class="section-label">OUR COMMITMENTS</div>
    <h2>What you can expect</h2>
    
    <div class="commitments-grid">
      <div class="commitment-card">
        <h3>Complete Code Ownership</h3>
        <p>You own every line of code, every database schema, every API endpoint from day one. No licensing fees. No vendor lock-in. You evolve independently.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="commitment-card">
        <h3>Production-Grade Engineering</h3>
        <p>Production systems. Architecture designed for scale, security, and reliability. Code reviews, testing, documentation built into every cycle.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="commitment-card">
        <h3>Integrated Intelligence</h3>
        <p>AI embedded where it creates measurable leverage. Better decisions. Less manual work. Patterns humans would miss. Not AI for AI's sake.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="commitment-card">
        <h3>Transparent Development</h3>
        <p>Weekly progress visibility. Code reviews shared with stakeholders. Direct access to the team. Architecture decisions explained and documented.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="commitment-card">
        <h3>Technical Partnership</h3>
        <p>Beyond handoff. Available for architecture consultation, integration challenges, scaling decisions. Your system grows—we grow with it.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="commitment-card">
        <h3>Scalable Architecture</h3>
        <p>Built to handle growth. Database architecture that scales. APIs that support high throughput. Security architecture for enterprise compliance.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ENGAGEMENT MODELS -->
  <section class="engagement-section">
    <div class="section-label">ENGAGEMENT MODELS</div>
    <h2>How we structure partnerships</h2>
    
    <div class="engagement-grid">
      <div class="engagement-card">
        <h3>Fixed-Scope Development</h3>
        <div class="engagement-detail">
          <div class="comparison-label">BEST FOR</div>
          <div class="comparison-text">New systems, major releases, internal tools.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="engagement-detail">
          <div class="comparison-label">STRUCTURE</div>
          <div class="comparison-text">Defined scope. Budget & timeline upfront.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="engagement-detail">
          <div class="comparison-label">ENGAGEMENT</div>
          <div class="comparison-text">Project-based. Payment upon completion.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="engagement-card">
        <h3>Ongoing Development</h3>
        <div class="engagement-detail">
          <div class="comparison-label">BEST FOR</div>
          <div class="comparison-text">SaaS platforms, competitive products, evolving systems.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="engagement-detail">
          <div class="comparison-label">STRUCTURE</div>
          <div class="comparison-text">Continuous partnership. Cycles adapt to priorities.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="engagement-detail">
          <div class="comparison-label">ENGAGEMENT</div>
          <div class="comparison-text">Monthly retainer. Collaborative roadmap.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="engagement-card">
        <h3>Strategic Partnership</h3>
        <div class="engagement-detail">
          <div class="comparison-label">BEST FOR</div>
          <div class="comparison-text">Founder-led products, enterprise infrastructure, systems central to advantage.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="engagement-detail">
          <div class="comparison-label">STRUCTURE</div>
          <div class="comparison-text">High-leverage. Embedded technical strategy.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="engagement-detail">
          <div class="comparison-label">ENGAGEMENT</div>
          <div class="comparison-text">Custom terms. Flexible. Deep partnership.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CLOSING CTA -->
  <section class="closing-section light-bg">
    <h2 id="contact">Ready to build?</h2>
    <p>Custom systems become the competitive advantage when they're built for your specific problem, your specific workflows, your specific logic. Every engagement begins with understanding—what you're building, what outcomes matter, what success looks like. Then engineering.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <button class="btn btn-primary">Start a project</button>
      <a href="/how-we-work" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn more about our approach →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  :root {
    --black: #000000;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --cyan: #0EA5E9;
    --text-muted: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    --text-secondary: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    --border-light: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  /* HERO SECTION */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    padding: 8rem 6% 6rem;
    min-height: 60vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    overflow: hidden;
    background-color: var(--black);
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .hero video {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .hero-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  /* BUTTONS */
  .btn {
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    font-weight: 500;
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background-color: var(--cyan);
    color: var(--black);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background-color: var(--white);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background-color: transparent;
    color: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--cyan);
    color: var(--cyan);
  }

  /* SECTIONS */
  section {
    padding: 6rem 6%;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }

  .light-bg {
    background-color: var(--white);
    color: var(--black);
  }

  .light-bg .section-label {
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }

  .light-bg h2,
  .light-bg h3,
  .light-bg h4 {
    color: var(--black);
  }

  .light-bg p {
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  h3 {
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  h4 {
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .emphasis {
    color: var(--cyan);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* INTRO SECTION */
  .intro-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .intro-text p {
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .intro-primary {
    font-size: 1.1rem !important;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8) !important;
    font-weight: 500 !important;
  }

  .image-placeholder {
    background-color: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    min-height: 400px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .image-placeholder-text {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .image-placeholder-text p {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  /* STATS SECTION */
  .stats-callout {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 3rem;
    margin: 3rem 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .stat-item {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--cyan);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .section-supporting-text {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  /* CAPABILITIES GRID */
  .capabilities-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .capability-card {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .capability-card:hover {
    background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-color: var(--cyan);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .capability-icon {
    background-color: rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    border-radius: 6px;
    height: 100px;
    width: 100px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .capability-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .capability-card p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .capability-details {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .detail-item {
